<BR>
I hereby challenge anyone on any server to get a group ... hell ... FIVE groups of level 60 (no less) players together and try to kill glox... sure, you may take him, but GOOD LUCK on getting out of cabalis alive... all of you.<BR>
<BR>
1: Guildmasters are built to be almost unkillable.<BR>
2: Attacking a guildmaster will cause most or all guards in the zone to come running.<BR>
3: When the guards come running, crusaders and troopers alike, expect to be Harm Touched at least once by each crusader that shows up for 700 points of damage PER HT.<BR>
4: Prepare to lose alot of exp and have fun getting your corpse back.<BR>
<BR>
Good luck and may Pain and Suffering guide your path.<BR>
<BR>
PS- Dont quote me on this, but if Glox does in fact get killed, will his corpse not go *POOF!* instantly, like it does with merchants?<BR>
<BR>
Oh yeah, and IMHO, if anything DOES drop off Glox it will be a hell of a lot better than what drops off any mob in Karnor.<BR>
